high_descs: Turn left and go toward the door and then turn left towards the white countertop.
Pick up the green and yellow dishsponge to the left of the black pot.
Turn left and go right around the cabinets to the front of the sink.
Put the dishsponge in the sink, rinse the dishsponge and pick it back up.
Put the dishsponge on the countertop to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean DishSponge on the CounterTop to the left of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the countertop across the room.
Take the dishsponge from the slab.
Take left,right turn and another right turn towards the sink.
Open the tap and wash the dishsponge in the sink.
Move away with the dishsponge from the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Wash the DishSponge and move with it to the CounterTop.

high_descs: Take the dish sponge in the table
Put the dish sponge in the sink, clean it off
Take back in the counter top
Place the dish sponge on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Take the dish sponge in the table Place the dish sponge on the counter top
